(26, 'LUMINA: The Immersive Art & Sound Experience', '2026-08-15', '18:00', 'The Fifth at Rockwell, Makati City', 'Festival / Expo', 'Step into a world where technology and audio collide. LUMINA is a one-night-only immersive festival featuring mind-bending visual projections, interactive 3D light installations, and live performances from top electronic and indie artists.\n\nWander through three distinct sensory zones: The Neon Garden, The Bass Cavern, and The Ambient Void. Take a break to enjoy curated street food and craft cocktails from our award-winning local vendors.\n\nWhether you are an art enthusiast, a tech geek, or just looking for an incredible night out with friends, LUMINA promises an unforgettable journey.', '1500', '🚨 Early bird tickets are almost gone! 18+ only. Valid ID required at the gates.', 38, 0, 'https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/026/794/640/large_2x/concert-stage-scenery-with-spotlights-colored-lights-smoke-free-photo.jpg', NULL, 800, 'Pending Approval'),
