(28, 'Future Innovators Tech Summit 2026', '2026-10-15', '08:00', 'SMX Convention Center, Mall of Asia Complex, Pasay City', 'Conference / Summit', 'Join the premier technology and innovation summit in Southeast Asia! The Future Innovators Tech Summit brings together industry leaders, visionary startup founders, and tech enthusiasts for a full day of immersive keynotes, panel discussions, and hands-on workshops.\n\nHighlights include:\n• AI & Machine Learning breakthroughs in modern business\n• The future of Web3 and decentralized applications\n• Networking sessions with top-tier venture capitalists\n• Exclusive access to the interactive Tech Expo floor\n\nWhether you are a seasoned developer, a business leader, or a student looking to break into the industry, this summit is your gateway to the forefront of digital transformation. Secure your spot today!', '2500', 'Early bird registrants get an exclusive VIP networking dinner pass. Strictly business casual attire inside the main halls.', 44, 0, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540575467063-178a50c2df87?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop', NULL, 1500, 'Published'),
